Happy New Year, nature lovers from all over the world! On the first day of 2023, CGTN Nature has a gift for you: the 2022 CGTN Nature Yearbook, which records the fantastic events of nature that you have experienced last year. Please follow Ge Ning's introduction, and review the happy moments you had with CGTN Nature. (Cover image designed by CGTN's Liu Shaozhen; Video edited by CGTN's Xu Chenlu.) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)